Popular Nollywood actor, Emmanuel Ehumadu better known as LaBista, has taken to social media to reveal scary thing he was offered at a barbecue groove. The renowned thespian made his surprise known in a recent post he shared on his verified Instagram page today, June 13. According to him, his Mexican friends invited him to a weekend Barbecue groove and he decided to attend. However, to his greatest surprise, he got served roasted and well garnished crocodile as Barbecue. Although he didn’t reveal whether or not he ate, he asked his fans what they would do if they were in his shoes. READ ALSO Disqualification: APC not fair to Obaseki – Babatope “And so I was invited to a weekend Barbecue groove by my Mexican Friends… and this is what I met. Abeg if na you; You go chop am?“